words.name: Scoring Reference Level
words.description: the target level used for scoring e.g. to define if a country is political correct and the range is 1 to 10, the treshold level could be at 7

words.name: Scoring Scaling Factor
words.description: the scaling factor for combining single factor to a total score, so a kind of weight, but in combination with the Scoring Reference Level

formulas.name: remaining travel interest
formulas.expression: = if ( "number of visits" = 0 ; 10 - "cultural equality" ; ( 10 - "cultural equality" ) / ( "number of visits" + 1 ) )

formulas.name: Travel Score
formulas.expression: = if ( "number of visits" = 0 ; 10 - "cultural equality" ; 10 - "cultural equality" / "cultural difference" - "number of visits" )
